                                Maecenas nec molestie quam. Morbi ornare egestas urna, in eleifend urna euismod 
                                sit amet. Nulla aliquam scelerisque enim, non commodo orci lobortis sit amet. 
                                Integer nec condimentum ipsum. Vivamus tempor auctor nulla, non aliquam risus venenatis a. 
                            <div id="author-link">
                                <p>View all posts by: <a rel="author" title="Posts by admin" href="#">admin</a></p>
                            </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>        
                </div>
             {% include "MainSiteBundle:Default:rightblock.html.twig" %}   
            </div>
          </div>
     </div>
</div>        
{% endblock %}